response.original_title: The Style Council - Far East & Far Out
response.overview: This DVD shows the band at their absolute best, and was shot in 1984 on a Japanese tour with a pack of dynamite hits already under their belt.  Tracklisting: 01. Intro. 02. Me Ship Came In. 03. The Big Boss Groove. 04. Here's One That Got Away. 05. You're The Best Thing. 06. It Just Came To Pieces In My Hands. 07. Mick's Up. 08. Dropping Bombs On The White House. 09. Long Hot Summer. 10. My Ever Changing Moods. 11. Le Depart. 12. The Whole Point Of No Return. 13. Money Go Around. 14. Headstart For Happiness. 15. Speak Like A Child. 16. Reprise - Le Depart.
response.title: The Style Council - Far East & Far Out
